        <updateDate>2006-04-18T21:18:12Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p> Stop the Automated Calls Act - Directs the Federal Trade Commission (FTC) to revise the do-not-call registry provisions of the Telemarketing Sales Rule to prohibit politically-oriented recorded message telephone calls to listed telephone numbers. </p> <p>Defines politically-oriented recorded message telephone call.</p>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
